{"abstract": "The personal care brand Burt\u2019s Bees is promoting anti-aging products in messages that will appear as appointments in electronic calendars.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2014/04/22/business/media/for-a-new-burts-bees-line-check-your-calendar.html", "snippet": "The personal care brand Burt\u2019s Bees is promoting anti-aging products in messages that will appear as appointments in electronic calendars.", "lead_paragraph": "WHILE it may seem that advertising is everywhere, one place marketers have not infiltrated is the popular calendar software on computers, smartphones and tablets. But now, in what Burt\u2019s Bees says is a marketing first, the natural personal care brand is introducing promotional messages that will appear as appointments in electronic calendars like those by Microsoft, Apple, Google and Yahoo.", "print_section": "B", "print_page": "3", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/04/22/business/Adco/Adco-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 640, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2014/04/22/business/Adco/Adco-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 640}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/04/22/business/Adco/Adco-jumbo.jpg", "height": 1024, "width": 961, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/04/22/business/Adco/Adco-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 2048, "width": 1921, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/04/22/business/Adco/Adco-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumbnail", "crop_name": "thumbStandard", "legacy